From Geoff Thomas Subject Re Help colors display in You'll probably have to set the palette up before you try drawing in the new Use the bios interrupt calls to set the r g b values in the range from for most cards for a particular palette colour in the range from for colour modes Then you should be able to draw pixels in those palette values and the result should be You might have to do a bit of colourmap compressing if you have more than unique rgb triplets for a colour Geoff Thomas Computer Science University of Canterbury Private Bag Christchurch Oook New Zealand